The paper deals with understanding and reasoning about cooking recipes, which involves multiple modalities such as text and images. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories such as natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and information retrieval (cs.IR). Among these, cs.CL and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories as they directly relate to the paper's focus on multimodal comprehension of text and images.
